From SILKWODJ at airproducts.com  Mon Sep  5 21:49:36 2011
From: SILKWODJ at airproducts.com (Silkworth,David J.)
Date: Mon, 5 Sep 2011 15:49:36 -0400
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Push back to a matrix (Noah Silverman)
